<sec xml:base="/std/iso/81286/en/chunks/id-5fd2afc4-64c3-409d-80d3-0a6b35594f8a.xml" sec-type="scope" id="id-5fd2afc4-64c3-409d-80d3-0a6b35594f8a"><title>Scope</title><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="deann.desai@gatech.edu" change-id="9f560286-d105-4d1a-c4dc-813f93fbb6f4" timestamp="1627655857746"?>This document provides guidelines to measure the status of energy management<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="9f560286-d105-4d1a-c4dc-813f93fbb6f4"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="571844" change-id="c224c5e6-ef62-4d6e-f65c-ff165446cd8c" timestamp="1633348302735"?> in an entity<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="c224c5e6-ef62-4d6e-f65c-ff165446cd8c"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="deann.desai@gatech.edu" change-id="19a8867b-5408-40e8-a91b-682798570177" timestamp="1627655857746"?>. The measurement results are described by using <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="19a8867b-5408-40e8-a91b-682798570177"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="571844" change-id="1ad9ba88-4db5-4d94-9e56-e4baa8ae2c6a" text="the " timestamp="1633348518755"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="deann.desai@gatech.edu" change-id="7ba1d543-e219-47cc-ba99-d36cdee6d0e7" timestamp="1627655857746"?>three scores: Structure Management Score (SMS), Operation Management Score (OMS) and Target Achievement Score (TAS).<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="7ba1d543-e219-47cc-ba99-d36cdee6d0e7"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="571844" change-id="b1c6241d-9616-4e0b-cbcd-390db8ffbd07" text="This document can be applied to organizations that have not yet implemented iso:pub:std:DIS:69426ISO 50001ISO 50001 to assist in identification of areas of performance improvement. It can also be applied by organizations that are already iso:pub:std:DIS:69426ISO 50001 conformant." timestamp="1633606634675"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="571844" change-id="a87abd22-36ea-4817-bbfa-44dc93dd6b17" timestamp="1633607269149"?>This document can be used by organizations that have an <std id="id-b2f8e07e-a9a1-40b3-f785-1a187ea6cd42"><std-id std-id-link-type="urn" std-id-type="undated">iso:pub:std:DIS:69426</std-id><std-ref>ISO 50001</std-ref></std>EnMS or those who have not yet implemented an EnMS. It can be used to identify areas for improvement or to identify areas in which improvement has taken place.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="a87abd22-36ea-4817-bbfa-44dc93dd6b17"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="deann.desai@gatech.edu" change-id="30ad8de6-4a89-42b7-a053-5c41b31c6667" timestamp="1627655857746"?>This document is applicable to an organization or association (e.g. national energy authorities) regardless of <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="30ad8de6-4a89-42b7-a053-5c41b31c6667"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="571844" change-id="2b8fea2b-2c43-4b58-f8d9-d5d4d99b6ef8" text="their" timestamp="1633348617824"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="571844" change-id="447227e9-8d31-444c-e5f7-5c8c0a25b4cb" timestamp="1633348618328"?>its<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="447227e9-8d31-444c-e5f7-5c8c0a25b4cb"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="deann.desai@gatech.edu" change-id="c7673166-88c7-43f6-d31a-a8ce45ed871f" timestamp="1627655857746"?> size, type or complexity, etc.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="c7673166-88c7-43f6-d31a-a8ce45ed871f"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="571844" change-id="383809bb-7f63-421a-b591-b621e23ad4f5" timestamp="1633616023227"?> This document as presented does not apply to countries, regions or cities.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="383809bb-7f63-421a-b591-b621e23ad4f5"?></p><p/><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="deann.desai@gatech.edu" change-id="f4ffc631-35df-4583-a688-4ada202bf42e" text="The Scope clause is a mandatory element of the text.For rules on the drafting of the Scope, refer to the ISO/IEC Directives, Part 2:2018, Clause 14." timestamp="1627655866526"?></sec>